room_title: Escape room "Eye Spy" by Panic Room CDA in Coeur d'Alene
room_address: 100 E Neider Ave Coeur d'Alene, ID 83815
room_description: It's been a year since Detective Mike Tuesday's death. After the reading of his will, there is still some cash unaccounted for. The heiress is getting impatient and wants her money. We need your brains to break into Mike's office and find what remains. You have 60 minutes to find the cash and get out before the crazy lady returns!
